{
  "stem": "2391.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she had no idea where he was, which was not the truth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she was desperate, because she was left without-- and she, she had planned to divorce him and we-- and start a new life, which, of course, was made up.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- but she had a big problem, a financial problem, because she had two children to raise.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the only way she would do-- she has a relative who was well-to-do, and he lived in Vichy-- in Vichy France.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he had invited her and-- to bring-- to bring the children for the time being.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he would take care of us, completely.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she said it was the only-- it was her only-- her only salvation and the only way she could-- she could survive the war.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But for this, she had to travel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She had to cross the demarcation line.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was the only-- the only big problem.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And for this, she would need a papers, you know, to cross the demarcation line.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he listened to her for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember when my mother stopped speaking, he--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] --he looked at her, for like, a minute, without saying a word.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother said she knew perfectly well that he didn't-- he didn't buy it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't buy a word of it, and he saw through her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then he finally says, well, I'll see what I can do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I want-- I want to warn you that as long as you stay here in the occupied territory, I could protect you.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We can protect you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We can do things for you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Once you cross the border, you realize that we are powerless?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have no influence anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother says, yes, I know that.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
